casebody.data:
STATE of North Carolina
v.
Librado BUSTOS. No. 609P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 3, 2007. Librado Bustos, Pro Se. Robert Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, G. Dewey Hudson, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 20th day of November 2006 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 3rd day of May 2007."
